ActBudget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 2
Budget Implementation Act, 2019, No. 1
SubjectOrder Fixing November 1, 2019 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the two Acts Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing November 1, 2019 as the day on which (1) Subdivision E of Division 7 of Part 4 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2018, NO. 2, chapter 27 of the Statutes of Canada, 2018, COMES INTO FORCE; and (2) sections 133 to 140 of the BUDGET IMPLEMENTATION ACT, 2019, NO. 1, chapter 29 of the Statutes of Canada, 2019, COMES INTO FORCE.
